Nonmuscle myosins IIA and IIB are present in adult motor nerve terminals.

Vega-Riveroll LJ(1), Wylie SR, Loughna PT, Parson SH, Chantler PD.

Author information:
(1)Royal Veterinary College, University of London, Royal College Street, London 
